{"tid":491884,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"謝安琪復出...當我無講過","createTime":"2017-12-07T03:26:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-07T17:01:07.000Z","uid":25653,"like":119,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"d1bc490c5129578ced9665579a655f8165d8f310","tid":491884,"uid":25653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T03:26:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/112514_56bcef8d0f199bf70643dd614bbc79a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F112514_56bcef8d0f199bf70643dd614bbc79a5.jpg&h=bf9f1436&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n老公阿聰被無綫封殺，Kay表示不用擔心，工作已有安排。<br />\n謝安琪（Kay）昨晚產後正式復工，於金鐘出現商場活動，身形依然圓潤，未回復最佳狀態，Kay說：「未算係全面復出，本來諗住下年中至尾，有合適工作先做。因為早咗復出，加快步伐做運動減肥，係意外收穫。阿聰（老公張繼聰）係運動狂熱，𠵱家有伴。」對於老公被無綫封殺，她笑說：「即刻收到好多慰問，又關心我哋生計，話要介紹工作，唔使擔心，工作有安排。」<br />\n有傳Kay以8位數字簽約麥浚龍公司，她即迴避指：「數字好複雜，呢啲數好難計。」之前她呻囡囡學發音只叫爸沒有媽，她笑說：「我已經用咗好多方法，佢都冇叫媽咪，好嬲呀！因為我係全職湊佢，見住我都叫爸爸，可能爸爸係佢前世情人，魅力沒法擋，冇辦法。」<br />\n採訪：卓寶花<br />\n攝影：林賓尼<br />\n<br />\n邊個敢話佢整過容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 臭男人嗰期個樣返晒黎 j開佢嘅死忠召喚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98fb615adba4d9bfe41dd7c69d56abab02dec887","tid":491884,"uid":133529,"like":191,"dislike":16,"score":175,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T04:18:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://mediumraw.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/3685sd-587x264.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmediumraw.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F11%2F3685sd-587x264.jpg&h=8c08a25b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67bb7315a74b6dbdebb9090f4e1ec7876df7309a","tid":491884,"uid":85819,"like":121,"dislike":5,"score":116,"citedBy":0,"replyTi